title: [NO/DK/SV/FI] Urusei Yatsura 2 - Beautiful Dreamer
description:
Great Anime film based on the TV-series "Urusei Yatsura" by Rumiko Takahashi. 

The night before the school festival, the earth is completely deserted and only a handful of people remains: Ataru and his friends. They enjoys this as their "ultimate summer vacation", but they soon start to remember the girl they all forgot... The girl who made this possible.

Genre: Anime, Animation, Comedy, Fantasy
Age Rating: 11 years and older
Runtime:  96 minutes
Studio: Kitty Films, Studio Pierrot
File format: .mkv
